Interface ILinTpConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable, IReferrable, ITpConfig

    public interface ILinTpConfig
extends IEntity, ITpConfig
    ILinTpConfig: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This element defines exactly one Lin TP Configuration. One LinTpConfig element shall be created for each Lin Network in the System.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
